{"type": "article", "id": 28428, "title": "看图：这里是过去那个周末发生的重要的事", "description": "每天我们都会摘取重要的新闻图片。PS：我们认为这个世界的重要性不应该有绝对的等级，重点是看得更多，探索更多。", "date": "2016-06-20T10:32:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29097, "name": "Color run"}, {"id": 6372, "name": "米兰男装周"}], "category": 5, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702150718dsemuMQBpvbf0DoV.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">          </p>\n<h2>过去的一段时间里，你需要知道的有：</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><b>1、民众持续悼念奥兰多枪击案遇难者</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150703o0bdzgZ9EIJOhctP.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Spencer Platt/Getty Images/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">美国奥兰多，当地民众持续悼念夜总会枪击案遇难者。<b><br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150704esRVvSdnHJBKp2y4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Adam Berry/Getty Images/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">德国柏林，悼念活动上一个藏在彩虹旗下的孩子。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>2、2016 欧洲杯</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150705PYZOinfFb9d0AkMW.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">FRANCISCO LEONG/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">法国巴黎，小组赛 F 组次轮，葡萄牙 0-0 奥地利。赛后 C 罗失落退场。<b><br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150705wxLKnpyTsdu3b9c2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68888889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Robert Pratta/路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">法国里昂，小组赛 A 组第 3 轮，罗马尼亚 0-1 阿尔巴尼亚。赛后巴沙抱爱女入场庆祝。<b><br></b></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>3、欧洲多国民众呼吁开放边境</b><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150706DW6ILq7VXhJzep2l.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.48611111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">法国与意大利边境，示威者组成人链，呼吁开放边境欢迎难民。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150707diaPMINkgXf9pSQj.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">JOSEP LAGO/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">西班牙巴塞罗那，民众呼吁欧洲当局为难民开放安全通道。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>4、意大利民众以吻反对英国脱欧</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150708VBX9TM7mqeZloHjw.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Remo Casilli/路透社/视觉中国 </div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">意大利罗马，人们在古斗兽场前亲吻，反对英国退出欧盟。英国将于 23 日举行全民公投，决定是否留在欧盟。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>5、冲绳民众集会抗议美军基地</b><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150708s5RubJm1yXiCSMGk.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Kyodo/路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">日本冲绳，当地民众参加反美军基地集会，抗议美军基地工作人员犯下的各种罪行。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>6、美国加州山火持续燃烧</b><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150709aZSWcYRrVMFJfle8.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">DAVID MCNEW/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">美国圣塔芭芭拉（Santa Barbara），当地森林大火持续燃烧，树木被消防飞机喷洒的阻燃剂染红。<b><br></b></p>\n<h2>除此之外，这些也值得一看：</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><b>1、2017 春夏米兰男装周</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150710rQl4nopiNe2P7GA0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">Dolce&amp;Gabbana 秀场。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150710pRUNJ85LKZbX2F1T.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Estrop/Getty Images/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">Versace 秀场。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150711qHbFaz1h0yQrkBxv.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Christian Vierig/Getty Images</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150712zAgj63CoKMXEHpiG.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Christian Vierig/Getty Images</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">米兰街头的时尚“潮人”们。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>2、北京举行彩色跑活动</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150714ugwDsyNMv1VkXTef.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p>北京，2016 彩色跑中国首站在北京丰台园博园开跑。 <br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>3、世界探戈锦标赛在哥伦比亚举行</b><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150714SdzaA14ETPxGiw7s.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">RAUL ARBOLEDA/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">哥伦比亚麦德林（Medellin），世界探戈锦标赛在当地举行。<b><br></b></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>4、</b><b>萨尔多瓦举行活雕塑比赛</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150715A69TLrNbYcoZpuaC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Jose Cabezas/路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">萨尔瓦多圣萨尔瓦多（San Salvador），选手参加“活雕塑”比赛。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>5、俄罗斯举行新娘游行</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150716keKXJP7EhpBQjbUY.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66018519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Mikhail Japaridze/TASS/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">俄罗斯莫斯科，年轻女性盛装打扮参加新娘游行。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>6、伦敦市长热气球比赛</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150718ndAh8G1yNEUL2tfF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">英国伦敦，一年一度的市长热气球比赛（Lord Mayor's Hot Air Balloon Regatta）举行，为市长基金募集善款。<br></p>\n\n"}